Name: Admin - Employee (DXI Agents)
BC Search Spec: u_contact.recordType=3 and exists (select isnull(a.attTXT01,'0') from u_contactAtt a where a.attINT01 = u_contact.id and a.attTXT01 > '0')

Name: CM Campaign
BC Search Spec: isnull(u_campaignHDR.diallerType,'') NOT IN ('SMS','Inbound Email') and u_campaignHDR.parentId=0 and ISNULL(u_campaignHdr.attTXT01,'')<>'OOHPolicy' and ISNULL(u_campaignHdr.atttxt02,'')<>'broadcastQ'

Name: CM Campaign Queue Nexmo
BC Search Spec: u_campaignHDR.parentId <> 0 AND u_campaignHDr.atttxt02 <> 'broadcastQ' AND 1 = (SELECT CASE WHEN c.[attTXT10] = 'tPointDial' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM u_campaignHDR c WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE c.[id] = u_campaignHDR.[parentId])

Name: CM Escalations
BC Search Spec: u_contact.recordType = 222 and u_contact.attINT01 in (select attINT01 from u_service with (nolock) where recordtype='CM Schedule' and attINT01 = u_contact.attINT01)

Name: CM In Email Campaign Agent INT
CM Inbound Numbers Available
BC Search Spec: u_inboundNumbers.id NOT IN (SELECT attINT01 FROM u_campaignhdrAtt WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE recordType = 'INBOUNDNUM')

Name: CM Media Activity
BC Search Spec: u_activity.actiontype in  ('Call Inbound' ,'Call Outbound' ,'Facebook Outbound' ,'Facebook Inbound' ,'Email Inbound' ,'Email Outbound' ,'SMS Transmission', 'SMS','SMS Inbound','SMS Outbound','DXI Call Outbound')

Name: CM Out of Hours Policy Rule
DXI - Raw Stats
BC Search Spec: convert(varchar, callid) in (select recordedfilename from u_activity)

Name: RM - Shift Cycle Item Team QTY
